item.minecraft.armor_stand.description: Use %s + %s with an empty hand to open configuration screen.
screen.alignments.statuemenus.block.desc: Align an armor stand placed on a surface so that a block held by it appears on the surface.
Align an armor stand placed on a surface so that a non-tool item held by it appears flat on the surface.
screen.alignments.statuemenus.floating_i: Align an armor stand placed on a surface so that an item held by it appears upright on the surface.
screen.alignments.statuemenus.tool.descr: Align an armor stand placed on a surface so that a tool held by it appears flat on the surface.
screen.style.statuemenus.invisible.descr: Makes the statue itself invisible, but still shows all equipped items.
screen.style.statuemenus.no_base_plate.d: Hide the stone base plate at the statue's feet.
screen.style.statuemenus.no_gravity.desc: Prevents the statue from falling down, so it may float freely.
screen.style.statuemenus.sealed.descript: The statue can no longer be broken, equipment cannot be changed. Disallows opening this menu in survival mode.
screen.style.statuemenus.show_arms.descr: Shows the statue's arms, so it may hold items in both hands.
screen.style.statuemenus.show_name.descr: Render the statue's name tag above it's head.
screen.style.statuemenus.small.descripti: Makes the statue half it's size like a baby mob.
statuemenus.screen.centered.description: Align an armor stand in the center of the block position it is placed on.
statuemenus.screen.cornered.description: Align an armor stand at the corner of the block position it is placed on.
statuemenus.screen.credits: Some content on this page originates from the Vanilla Tweaks "Armor Statues" data pack. Click this button to go to their website!
statuemenus.screen.rotations.pose.head: Head
statuemenus.screen.rotations.tip1: Hold any [§dShift§r] or [§dAlt§r] key to lock two-dimensional sliders to a single axis while dragging!
statuemenus.screen.rotations.tip2: Use arrow keys to move sliders with greater precision than when dragging! Focus a slider first by clicking.
statuemenus.screen.style.name: Set a name to display above the entity if enabled.
